{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"0db51bd28d535467","type":"text","text":"# 📋 economics-video\n\n经济学YouTube频道长视频全自动生产流程。 流程：选题探讨 → Gemini Deep Research → Grok Expert 口播文案 → TTS 配音 → Whisper 字幕 → Grok 字幕校对 → 配图规划。 核心价值：深度研究（系统级洞察）、口播文案（优雅叙事）、配图规划（视觉叙事）。 风格约束：深度叙事+系统思维+高阶美学，非工具化生存指南，18-22分钟英文口播。 自动化：Grok/Gemini 通过 Playwright skill 调用，TTS/Whisper 本地执行。","x":0,"y":-40,"width":900,"height":182,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"22054b0a1a65227f","type":"text","text":"📄 `prompts/script-prompt.md`","x":30,"y":724,"width":360,"height":56,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"topic_discuss","type":"text","text":"## topic_discuss\n\n🤖 `claude-code`   🔴 `ask`\n\n和用户讨论确定视频主题、切入角度和目标受众\n\n📤 `topic.md`","x":460,"y":212,"width":440,"height":173,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"deep_research","type":"text","text":"## deep_research\n\n🤖 `claude-code`   🟡 `report`\n\n用 Prompt 1 通过 Gemini Deep Research 对主题进行系统级深度研究。 调用 gemini skill 的 start_research 发起研究，轮询 get_research_report 获取完整报告。\n\n📤 `research.md`","x":460,"y":455,"width":440,"height":199,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"write_script","type":"text","text":"## write_script\n\n🤖 `claude-code`   🔴 `ask`\n\n用 Prompt 2 + 研究报告通过 Grok Expert 写 18-22 分钟英文口播文案。 调用 grok skill 的 chat action，model 选 expert。\n\n📤 `script.md`","x":460,"y":724,"width":440,"height":189,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"voiceover","type":"text","text":"## voiceover\n\n⚙️ `script`   🟢 `auto`\n\n用 edge-tts 将英文文案转为高质量语音音频\n\n`python scripts/tts.py --input {run.dir}/script.md --output {run.dir}/voiceover.mp3`\n\n📤 `voiceover.mp3`","x":460,"y":983,"width":440,"height":216,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"transcribe","type":"text","text":"## transcribe\n\n⚙️ `script`   🟢 `auto`\n\n用 faster-whisper 将语音转为带时间戳的 SRT 粗字幕\n\n`python scripts/transcribe.py --input {run.dir}/voiceover.mp3 --output {run.dir}/raw_subtitles.srt`\n\n📤 `raw_subtitles.srt`","x":460,"y":1269,"width":440,"height":222,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"correct_subtitles","type":"text","text":"## correct_subtitles\n\n🤖 `claude-code`   🟡 `report`\n\n用 Grok 根据原文校对粗字幕中的识别错误，保持时间戳不变，生成干净的 SRT。 将粗字幕 + 原文一起发给 Grok，要求逐行校对后输出完整 SRT。\n\n📤 `subtitles.srt`","x":460,"y":1561,"width":440,"height":182,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"plan_images","type":"text","text":"## plan_images\n\n🤖 `claude-code`   🔴 `ask`\n\n根据字幕每个时间段的内容，为每段生成适配的图片生成 prompt。 将完整字幕文件发给 Grok/Gemini，让它为每个 5-10 秒段落写出视觉氛围和具体画面描述。 输出 JSON 格式：[{time_range, subtitle_text, image_prompt}]。\n\n📤 `image_plan.json`","x":460,"y":1813,"width":440,"height":208,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"ce08b83024867f6a","type":"text","text":"📄 `prompts/research-prompt.md`","x":30,"y":455,"width":360,"height":56,"color":"3"}
	],
